{"tid":315489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦肯頓市集發生大火　目擊者：「瘋狂的景象」","createTime":"2017-07-10T05:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T05:35:28.000Z","uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"166cde386dd9bd5bf0d1ea4c990bb11fb4228d4d","tid":315489,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/694005/xlarge/14dfa2e35552287ca51f88f7ade7097a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F694005%2Fxlarge%2F14dfa2e35552287ca51f88f7ade7097a.jpg&h=1c80b6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/693780/xlarge/bd3ade4cf655d847e693d86c6bdf2aa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F693780%2Fxlarge%2Fbd3ade4cf655d847e693d86c6bdf2aa3.jpg&h=ed1e93ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國倫敦旅遊熱點肯頓市集（Camden Market）7月10日凌晨發生大火，倫敦消防局在Twitter上持續更新有關大火資料。從現場圖片可見火勢十分猛烈，橙紅火光照亮整個夜空，伴隨黑煙直撲附近民居。<br />\n<br />\n大火發生後附近街坊紛紛上載照片及影片到社交網絡，有人指火光遠至數哩都清晰可見。警方呼籲民眾不要前往該處。<br />\n<br />\n名為Joan Ribes的目擊者稱，目睹大火後隨即報警。她說大火看來很危險，火舌直撲半空到附近地方。她說大火蔓延得很快，擔心建築物隨時會爆炸。該處附近有餐廳及廚房。<br />\n<br />\n三層大廈被通頂　火場現已受控<br />\n<br />\n路透社消息報道，消防共派出10架消防車與70個消防員在場撲救，火場現已受控。據悉其中一幢起火大廈，三層連天花已被燒至通頂，附近亦有少量蔓延跡象。<br />\n<br />\n該區2008年曾發生大火，導致市集一大部分焚毀，需連續關閉好幾個月進行維修。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/693737/xlarge/3799def3ec6e1dfdaf4d0317396cef43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F693737%2Fxlarge%2F3799def3ec6e1dfdaf4d0317396cef43.jpg&h=b277f3e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><br />\n目擊者：「瘋狂、瘋狂的景象」</strong><br />\n<br />\n倫敦消防局在Twitter上持續更新有關市集大火的最新消息，指市集內一幢建築物着火，一樓、二樓、三樓及天台已陷入火海。<br />\n<br />\n22歲目擊者Billy Dunmore向《衛報》表示：「我與朋友行經市集，看到路旁冒出黑煙。我看到Honest Burger的窗戶冒出火舌。我通過玻璃窗反映，看到市集內很多火陷。」<br />\n<br />\n另有一名目擊者在Twitter推文說：「剛駕車經過肯頓市集，一幢建築物上有大火。它接近Loch Bridge！瘋狂、瘋狂的景象。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/103652/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E-%E8%82%AF%E9%A0%93%E5%B8%82%E9%9B%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%E5%8F%97%E6%8E%A7-%E7%9B%AE%E6%93%8A%E8%80%85-%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82%E7%9A%84%E6%99%AF%E8%B1%A1-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F103652%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E6%2597%2585%25E9%2581%258A%25E7%2586%25B1%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E8%2582%25AF%25E9%25A0%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25AB%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%2593%258A%25E8%2580%2585-%25E7%2598%258B%25E7%258B%2582%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2599%25AF%25E8%25B1%25A1-&d=f%2BQVzLxqOPmwvy0z%2BjW7Lu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=e7c9f078\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/103652/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E7%86%B1%E9%BB%9E-%E8%82%AF%E9%A0%93%E5%B8%82%E9%9B%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%AB%E5%8F%97%E6%8E%A7-%E7%9B%AE%E6%93%8A%E8%80%85-%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82%E7%9A%84%E6%99%AF%E8%B1%A1-</a>"},{"pid":"be32a743bd5177b15a1a784d38da9b7a10d85c16","tid":315489,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"Crazy People<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線市集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9efbefd03d7ddcba79eb3193ae945733854c84","tid":315489,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"又恐襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db837651eff0e862d95fa975ca875a35f35be5a2","tid":315489,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T05:26:40.000Z","msg":"等睇LIHKG災難應變專家講解必勝求生法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf7b6fa276aaa3f5d6a930c4985a8ec69a71284","tid":315489,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s